      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCHINVAR THOR (2) was well fancied as favourite latest and led for much of the way but faded to place, beaten half a length (25.37) at this track in a Restricted WIN H over 450m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Winning claims. HOOKED AND HAPPY (3) goes very well this trip starting 10 times for four wins and three minors. Comes off a (25.40) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Restricted WIN H over 450m at this track. Among the main chances. SHADE OF PALE (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (25.61) at this track behind HOOKED AND HAPPY in a Restricted WIN H. Gave a start buy found the line well late. Expected to be in the finish again. PAW ORENTHAL (6) won last start in very good time. Hard to beat again.",
